description: Redevelopment of Bunns Lane car park (Mill Hill) for the erection of buildings up to 4-6 storeys in height, comprising up to 130 residential units (Class C3) along with roof terraces and external amenity space, reprovision of 38 car parking spaces, cycle parking, landscaping, alterations to the existing vehicular and pedestrian access, and other associated works.

phasing_details.phase_detail: Entire Development with planned completion in April 2028

site_name: Bunns Lane Car ParkBunns LaneLondonNW7
